sequenceDiagram
 participant U as User
 participant A as 🅰 Angular App
 participant API as ASP.NET Core API
 participant DB as SQLite DB
 participant OM as OpenMeteo API
 
 U->>A: Access Weather App
 A->>API: GET /api/weather
 API->>DB: Query weather data
 DB-->>API: Return stored data
 API-->>A: Weather data response
 A-->>U: Display weather table
 
 U->>A: Click "Load Live Data"
 A->>API: GET /api/weather/live
 API->>OM: Fetch current weather
 OM-->>API: Weather data
 API-->>A: Live weather data
 A-->>U: Display live data
 
 U->>A: Click "Save to Database"
 A->>API: POST /api/weather
 API->>DB: Insert weather data
 DB-->>API: Confirm save
 API-->>A: Success response
 A-->>U: Show success message